peg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623104602aK5Ohg7BdZl0nqPu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201706231046020qgRpPQoBcsXZnID.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623104602kyvEiH4DpswPrYgd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623104602qNMCS5ReUlci30B4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623104603u1PMqpQiWtvAb8YT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623104603OQogcY2srXv6e1Zd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623104603WCcrlXgknYmRhGeK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623104603Pf7b3i6dTxDGO98e.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623104604AYieXkIlRFQCVp3K.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623104604ONrugPFwH901zxtC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623104604zWhXcyZP1mKO2sIE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623104604tF2Mqv9bx05iXw6A.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623104605RPbjwl4nVy7MB8Sq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623104605znZD20BQGRpw3WIO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623104604w9mvCu0HUg26cTNA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623104605ZcVb06pXk8GDRN7L.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623104605cIzAabKeBfPFt6Wx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623104605Up6WYkg8ZcSvlRuj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623104606PqHu15gSDyX98pIf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/6/starbucks\" rel=\"nofollow\">星巴克将在京都的清水寺附近开设全新门店。</a>新店的前身是栋有百年历史的日式老宅，星巴克把它改成了世界第一间可以坐在榻榻米上喝咖啡的星巴克，原本的建筑结构和外型都得到了保留。 </p><p>这家店将于 6 月 30 日正式开幕。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623101734yrfv2561EGWaqATD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623101734r48OfSMaTX6WnPdg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667075\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>庆祝 Converse 一百年，同时也是《赛文奥特曼》公开播放 50 周年，<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/6/converse-all-star-x-ultra-seven\" rel=\"nofollow\">Converse 要与《赛文奥特曼》联手推出日本限定版 All Star。</a></p><p>这款鞋的鞋身完全照着超人七号制服配色的红色与金属银制作，鞋垫上还印着即将迎战的赛文奥特曼，另外还搭配了特制的奥特曼礼盒。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201706231017246usldkC9Sp4eLXIg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623101713V71BYuatWxnF6iDq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623101713Elg7tCfxwWvXp3Od.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623101713yh1aV46Zob2p8Rsi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667647\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623101718I1A5zEh9VT6MxPuJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/fendi-capsule-collection-taeyang-10924250/\" rel=\"nofollow\">FENDI 与韩国流行偶像、BIG BANG 组合的 TaeYang 合作，推出名为「FENDI for TaeYang」的全新联名系列。</a>该系列围绕雏菊元素展开，包括夹克、卫衣和 T 恤等服饰单品，还有背包、手包、球鞋和钥匙扣在内的丰富配饰。 </p><p>全新系列将于 7 月 27 日率先在香港发售，售价从 400 到 8500 欧元不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201706231017001RuGOH27I3Sn8Apx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666884\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623101700j0DrXPlQKNCpW2Ex.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>从今天开始，你能在 colette 二楼 Balenciaga 的快闪店内，买到<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/06/22/balenciaga-biycle-ss18-colette/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Balenciaga 的自行车</a>了。这款单车只限 colette 发售，定价为 3500 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623101649eyZ5RguEwa2c4kNx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：<a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/mergers-acquisitions/investor-msgm-contemporary-label-style-capital-10926480/\" rel=\"nofollow\">wwd</a></p>"}